Subject: Re: [T2] Oil Leak and Valve Cover Gaskets

At 09:01 PM 8/16/2008, Jason Meyer wrote...
>My question is, with the installation of new gaskets, can their "life" 
>and
>integrity be extended

I use sealant (Hylomar) between the gasket and the cover, but only a 
wipe of grease between the gasket and the head. When putting them back 
on, move them around a bit to find where they settle and fit best (when 
the compressed gasket material seats where it was before).
